{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"三反肃反中的写照（诗）","authors":["姜子惠","重庆"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":5}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"三反肃反中的写照（诗）","type":"title"},{"text":"重庆姜子惠","type":"authors"},{"text":"[原编者按：姜子惠，男，25岁，地主出身，父母均被管制，姜在重庆市税务局工作。]","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"（一）","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"无事捕风捉影，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"凭空兴风作浪，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有意制造假老虎，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"那管他人冤枉。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"寄言积极分子，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"其实狼肺狗肠，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"只为升级拿票子，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不惜丧心病狂。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"（二）","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"生平不喜逢迎，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"至始最恨诌媚，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"纵然有才又有德，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"总不被人尝识，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"提薪提级无望，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"落后分子有你，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"几年还是起码级，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"怎不叫人掩（咽）气。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第二集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}